title: Private balconies on floors 2 and above, Hiking trails nearby
posting_body: This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1070 Sq.
The Village at Ten Trails is a community within a community.

Live amid the stunning natural beauty of the Pacific Northwest, with wooded trails, parks, a town center with retail village, a school and residences all combining to create an interactive atmosphere.
We like to call it your new hometown.
Apartment homes ranging from one to three bedrooms are now pre-leasing, offering high-end finishes, thoughtful touches and comfortable spaces to make your own.

Quartz countertops, Electric fireplaces (in select homes), Oversized windows, Private balconies on floors 2 and above, Stainless steel appliances, In-home washer and dryer, 9-foot ceilings (18 feet on top floor)
Centrally located between Maple Valley, Covington, Kent and Enumclaw, Playgrounds, Community events, Hiking trails nearby, Wave Broadband Gigabit Internet Access, Future retail, Picnic areas
